data.description: Stylish one story brick home with upgraded light fixtures and paint. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by beautiful flooring that spans throughout the common areas, creating a seamless and elegant look.  The heart of this home is the modern open kitchen, featuring granite counters, a large island that serves as a focal point for both cooking and gathering. With plenty of storage space, this kitchen is a chef's dream, providing you with all the room you need to store your culinary essentials. The spacious bedrooms are designed for comfort and relaxation, with ample natural light streaming in to create a warm and welcoming atmosphere. Whether you're unwinding in the primary suite or hosting guests, these bedrooms offer the perfect retreat. Check out the 3D walkthrough!    Step outside to the covered patio, where you can enjoy outdoor living year-round. Don't miss your opportunity to experience all that this beautiful property has to offer. Schedule your showing now!
